    },
    "RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) is a technology that enables AI to access project code.\n\nWorkflow:\n1. Index project files\n2. Search for relevant code when user asks questions\n3. AI answers based on the found code\n\nThis allows AI to accurately answer questions about your project." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) is a technology that enables AI to access project code.\n\nWorkflow:\n1. Index project files\n2. Search for relevant code when user asks questions\n3. AI answers based on the found code\n\nThis allows AI to accurately answer questions about your project."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) 是一种让 AI 能够查阅项目代码的技术。\n\n工作流程:\n1. 索引项目文件\n2. 用户提问时搜索相关代码\n3. AI 基于找到的代码回答问题\n\n这样 AI 就能准确回答关于你项目的问题了。"
          }
        },
        "zh-HK" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) 是一種讓 AI 能夠查閱項目代碼的技術。\n\n工作流程:\n1. 索引項目文件\n2. 用戶提問時搜索相關代碼\n3. AI 基於找到的代碼回答問題\n\n這樣 AI 就能準確回答關於你項目的問題了。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
